  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK949">
<l>uṟṟā ṉaḷavum piṇiyaḷavuṅ kālamuṅ</l>
<l>kaṟṟāṉ karutic ceyal</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The learned (physician) should ascertain the condition of his patient; the nature of his disease, and the season (of the year) and (then) proceed (with his treatment).</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
